00048 void CHPFileWriterTest::WriteExpressionTest()
00049 {
00050         CHPData data("CHP_expression_file", CHP_EXPRESSION_ASSAY_TYPE);
00051         data.SetEntryCount(2, 16, true);
00052         data.SetBackgroundZoneCnt(2);
00053         writer = new CHPFileWriter(data);
00054 
00055         CHPExpressionEntry e1("probe set 1",10,11.0f,17.8f,6,5,true,2,56.9f,45.89f,42.0f,47.0f,2);
00056         CHPExpressionEntry e2("probe set 2",10,1.0f,7.8f,6,5,true,2,5.9f,4.89f,2.0f,7.0f,2);
00057         writer->SeekToDataSet();
00058         writer->WriteExpressionEntry(e1);
00059         writer->WriteExpressionEntry(e2);
00060 
00061         CHPBackgroundZone bgz1(11.0f,17.8f,56.9f,45.89f);
00062         CHPBackgroundZone bgz2(1.0f,7.8f,6.9f,5.89f);
00063         writer->SeekToBgSet();
00064         writer->WriteBackgroundZone(bgz1);
00065         writer->WriteBackgroundZone(bgz2);
00066         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(1);
00067 
00068         delete writer;
00069 
00070 
00071         CHPFileReader reader;
00072         reader.SetFilename("CHP_expression_file");
00073         CHPData data2;
00074         reader.Read(data2);
00075 
00076         CHPExpressionEntry e;
00077         data2.GetEntry(0, e);
00078         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetProbeSetName() == e1.GetProbeSetName());
00079         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetSignal(), e1.GetSignal(), 0.000001f);
00080         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetDetectionPValue(), e1.GetDetectionPValue(), 0.000001f);
00081         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetChangePValue(), e1.GetChangePValue(), 0.000001f);
00082         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetSigLogRatio(), e1.GetSigLogRatio(), 0.000001f);
00083         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetSigLogRatioLo(), e1.GetSigLogRatioLo(), 0.000001f);
00084         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetSigLogRatioHi(), e1.GetSigLogRatioHi(), 0.000001f);
00085         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetDetection() ==e1.GetDetection());
00086         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetNumPairs() ==e1.GetNumPairs());
00087         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetNumPairsUsed() ==e1.GetNumPairsUsed());
00088         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetHasComparisonData() ==e1.GetHasComparisonData());
00089         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetChange() ==e1.GetChange());
00090         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetCommonPairs() ==e1.GetCommonPairs());
00091 
00092         data2.GetEntry(1, e);
00093         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetProbeSetName() == e2.GetProbeSetName());
00094         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetSignal(), e2.GetSignal(), 0.000001f);
00095         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetDetectionPValue(), e2.GetDetectionPValue(), 0.000001f);
00096         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetChangePValue(), e2.GetChangePValue(), 0.000001f);
00097         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetSigLogRatio(), e2.GetSigLogRatio(), 0.000001f);
00098         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetSigLogRatioLo(), e2.GetSigLogRatioLo(), 0.000001f);
00099         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.GetSigLogRatioHi(), e2.GetSigLogRatioHi(), 0.000001f);
00100         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetDetection() ==e2.GetDetection());
00101         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetNumPairs() ==e2.GetNumPairs());
00102         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.GetNumPairsUsed() ==e2.GetNumPairsUsed());

00242 {
00243         CHPData data("CHP_reseq_file", CHP_RESEQUENCING_ASSAY_TYPE);
00244         data.SetEntryCount(5, 10);

00251         CHPReseqEntry e;
00252         e.call = 'a';

00256         e.score = 2.0f;
00257         writer->WriteReseqEntry(e);
00258         e.call = 'g';
00259         e.score = 3.0f;
00260         writer->WriteReseqEntry(e);
00261         e.call = 't';
00262         e.score = 4.0f;
00263         writer->WriteReseqEntry(e);
00264         e.call = 'n';
00265         e.score = 5.0f;
00266         writer->WriteReseqEntry(e);
00267 
00268         writer->SeekToForceSet();
00269         CHPReseqForceCall force;
00270         force.position = 1;
00271         force.call = 'a';
00272         force.reason = CC_SATURATION_LEVEL_FORCE_CALL;
00273         writer->WriteForceCall(force);
00274         force.position = 2;
00275         force.call = 'c';
00276         force.reason = CC_WEAK_SIGNAL_THR_FORCE_CALL;
00277         writer->WriteForceCall(force);
00278 
00279         writer->SeekToOrigCallSet();
00280         CHPReseqOrigCall orig;
00281         orig.position = 3;
00282         orig.call = 't';
00283         writer->WriteOrigCall(orig);
00284         orig.position = 4;
00285         orig.call = 'a';
00286         writer->WriteOrigCall(orig);
00287         orig.position = 5;
00288         orig.call = 'g';
00289         writer->WriteOrigCall(orig);
00290 
00291         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(1);
00292 
00293         delete writer;
00294 
00295 
00296 
00297 
00298         CHPFileReader reader;
00299         reader.SetFilename("CHP_reseq_file");
00300         CHPData data2;
00301         reader.Read(data2);
00302 
00303         data2.GetEntry(0, e);
00304         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.call == 'a');
00305         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.score, 1.0f, 0.0001f);
00306 
00307         data2.GetEntry(1, e);
00308         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.call == 'c');
00309         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(e.score, 2.0f, 0.0001f);
00310
